He tried to shoot me,

392
00:16:37,450 --> 00:16:39,490
but ... Anyway, he ran away and drove off.

393
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:42,760
Well then, he drove off,

394
00:16:43,050 --> 00:16:44,870
so who tied you up and beat you?

395
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:45,850
The dealer.

396
00:16:46,340 --> 00:16:48,120
I called him up. I told him what happened.

397
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:50,320
Next thing I know, he's in my office punching me,

398
00:16:50,530 --> 00:16:51,870
calling me a thief.

399
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:53,200
All right, what's the dealer's name?

400
00:16:56,570 --> 00:16:57,630
A little girl got shot

401
00:16:57,630 --> 00:17:00,160
'cause you were hiding drug money in a church.

402
00:17:00,830 --> 00:17:03,220
So you need to start talking now.

403
00:17:06,080 --> 00:17:07,820
Carlos, I don't care about you,

404
00:17:07,820 --> 00:17:10,550
the cash, the priest, or the church.

405
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,060
I just wanna find the guy

406
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:16,040
who did the robbery and shot that little girl.

407
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:19,030
Now you ask me, we're on the same side on this thing, bro.

408
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,610
What are you saying?

409
00:17:21,210 --> 00:17:24,170
I'm saying I'll find him, and then I'll put him in prison,

410
00:17:24,170 --> 00:17:25,270
and I'm done.

411
00:17:26,150 --> 00:17:28,680
You're free to do whatever you gotta do.

412
00:17:31,260 --> 00:17:33,570
Okay, who else knew about the money?

413
00:17:33,570 --> 00:17:34,240
Nobody.

414
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:36,170
No friends? Business associates?

415
00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:37,810
They all criminals, man.

416
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:40,120
Why would I tell them where I hide my cash?

417
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:42,620
So you telling me only you and Father Allende

418
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:44,010
