419
00:17:44,010 --> 00:17:45,860
Yeah, that's why I beat his ass.

420
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:47,290
He's playing me like a fool.

421
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:50,130
No. His story checks out.

422
00:17:50,390 --> 00:17:52,590
After the guy took the money, he ran out,

423
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:55,510
Allende chased after him, tackled the guy.

424
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:58,770
He turned around, got off two shots, almost killed the priest.

425
00:17:58,770 --> 00:18:00,900
Got the whole thing on tape too.

426
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:02,770
Sound like an inside job to you?

427
00:18:05,210 --> 00:18:07,740
So who else knew about the money in the church?

428
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:09,760
I'm telling you, man, I don't know.

429
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:13,680
All right, listen.

430
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:16,760
If you think of something that might be useful,

431
00:18:16,930 --> 00:18:18,110
give me a call.

432
00:18:23,050 --> 00:18:24,350
We got a hit on that black car?

433
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:26,430
Yeah, pulled video from a traffic cam

434
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,620
two blocks south of the church.

435
00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:28,560
You run the plates?

436
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:31,530
Yep, it came back to a 2004 Grand Cherokee.

437
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:34,470
It's registered to a female Hispanic, 29 years of age.

438
00:18:34,610 --> 00:18:36,620
She goes by the name Anna Salgado.

439
00:18:36,760 --> 00:18:39,160
She lives at 6438 South Homan,

440
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:40,620
